snippet.title: Lost Paws Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as a stray dog in an open-world survival game! Run, jump, dig, and bonk through a vast city and its surrounding areas. Meet new people and learn new abilities as you search for a way home. How you play determines how the world will play with you. What kind of doggo will you be?

Get Lost Paws on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2027590/Lost_Paws/
